WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
<v Narrator>Welcome to RestoreAssist. Let's create your first inspection.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
<v Narrator>Click New Inspection in the top right, then select the claim type — water damage, mould, fire, or general.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
<v Narrator>Enter the property address. RestoreAssist will geocode it and create a digital twin.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
<v Narrator>Add photos, moisture readings, and notes. Each entry is timestamped and tamper-evident.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
<v Narrator>When you're done, click Submit. The AI will generate a professional S500-compliant report.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
<v Narrator>Your inspection is now part of the chain of custody, ready for insurer review.
